1.The weights are saved in each epoch if `no_val=True`. https://github.com/Tramac/Fast-SCNN-pytorch/blob/a197f5e734632cb80798c90e825dcfdafd8422d9/train.py#L150
2.resume the model. https://github.com/Tramac/Fast-SCNN-pytorch/blob/a197f5e734632cb80798c90e825dcfdafd8422d9/train.py#L94
